					<msContents>
						<summary>

						<p>This registers an endowment of land tax-free, for the (maintenance of the) priests performing worship in the temple of Paramēśvara at Tiruppaḻūr, by Araṅgaṉ Veṇṇāval of Kāraikkuḍi in Viḷattūr-nāḍu. The land seems to have needed some improvement which was left to be effected by the beneficiary.</p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
